    <item>
      <title>Solitude Is a One-Person Celebration; Celebration Is a Crowd’s Loneliness</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/en/posts/loneless-and-crowd/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Nov 2025 20:17:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/en/posts/loneless-and-crowd/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;slug: loneless-and-crowd&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h1 id=&#34;solitude-is-a-one-person-celebration-celebration-is-a-crowds-loneliness&#34;&gt;Solitude Is a One-Person Celebration; Celebration Is a Crowd’s Loneliness&lt;a href=&#34;#solitude-is-a-one-person-celebration-celebration-is-a-crowds-loneliness&#34; class=&#34;heading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Link to this section&#34;&gt;&lt;svg class=&#34;h-4 w-4&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34;&gt;&lt;g fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34;&gt;&lt;path d=&#34;M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71&#34;/&gt;&lt;path d=&#34;M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71&#34;/&gt;&lt;/g&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;h2 id=&#34;idolization&#34;&gt;Idolization&lt;a href=&#34;#idolization&#34; class=&#34;heading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Link to this section&#34;&gt;&lt;svg class=&#34;h-4 w-4&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34; viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34;&gt;&lt;g fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34;&gt;&lt;path d=&#34;M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71&#34;/&gt;&lt;path d=&#34;M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71&#34;/&gt;&lt;/g&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Yes—&lt;br&gt;&#xA;I never really had idols growing up.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
